widgets_values:
for guiders : you can try stg-8 step, stg-13 step or cfg-guider  (connect to "guider entry point" on first pass)
for sigmas  : sigmas-13step, sigmas-8step or simple sigmas node. (connect to "sigmas easing" node)

you have match step count if you are using any of the stg nodes. they take longer but better quality.

(of course you can also change samplers in all three stages to your choice)
